These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, punk
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, turquise
1. the person who likes turquise is in an odd position##4
2. the fan punk and the person who likes turquise have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |
| Food    | punk | soul  |
| Sport   | turquise    | red |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-2::.
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, chinchilla
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, lilac
1. the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who likes orange have the same parity positions##9
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |     2     |
| Beverage   | chinchilla      | guinea-pig       |
| Food       | lilac | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, ship
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, horror
1. the person driving the bike and the person watching animation movies have different parity positions##9
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | ship     | bike       |
| Sport         | animation | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, bolivar
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
2. the person who growsballoon-flower and the bolivar-smoker have different parity positions##9
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Nationality   | balloon-flower | begonia |
| Sport         | dannemann | bolivar  |

 #################################

 
